{"tid":1510413,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"夾娃娃機看文化差異：台灣教你再厲害也玩不過潛規則，日本告訴你「努力就會有收穫」","createTime":"2019-08-27T07:26:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T10:16:53.000Z","uid":22675,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"ad3c2e1788de10b406d3f5fcde8db8f96101c844","tid":1510413,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T07:26:22.000Z","msg":"【為什麼挑選這篇文章】<br />\n<br />\n台灣和日本都有夾娃娃機，但在台灣夾娃娃機幾乎是一場騙局，台灣夾娃娃機只會教你「你永遠都玩不贏商家、交保證金就好了」，但日本娃娃機普遍來說就能體驗可能撿便宜、挑戰成功夾中的樂趣&mdash;&mdash;這倒不是日本太好，而是台灣的情況太過惡劣。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://buzzorange.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/2897476052_4e418c5388_z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbuzzorange.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F02%2F2897476052_4e418c5388_z.jpg&h=d5153509&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n抓娃娃機，是台日兩國很常見的娛樂機器。<br />\n<br />\n而且也是相當能凸顯出兩國文化差異以至於國力落差的好象徵。<br />\n<br />\n有玩過台灣娃娃機的人都知道，幾乎絕大多數商家都會把夾子調鬆，鬆到比穿了十年的大學系服領口還鬆，然後賭偶然一次正常緊的機率。<br />\n<br />\n廣告<br />\n<br />\n因為爭議太大，後來還搞出「保證取物」的規定，只要投到一定金額，就夾到取出為止。當然，怎麼算商家都不會虧。<br />\n<br />\n但是日本就完全不同，憑真本事，只要你技術夠好，就絕對可能用低於成本的價錢，夾到娃娃。不會有夾子很鬆這種鬼事情。<br />\n<br />\n台灣的夾娃娃機，讓你學到一件事情：你永遠都玩不贏商家。即使你技術好，真的夾中，但是當夾子升起時，娃娃仍然會落下。<br />\n<br />\n廣告<br />\n<br />\n這樣還會有人想練自己的技術嗎？完全沒有用嘛，直接繳保護費才是重點。像不像披著自由競爭假象的潛規則？然後層面放大一點來看，這個國家會有真正的夾娃娃達人嗎？我看只會有繳保護費達人吧。<br />\n<br />\n更不用說，這種穩贏的做生意方法，其實只會讓自己的總體營收是下降的：我直接去買還比較便宜。夾娃娃機的誘因有兩個：可能撿到便宜，以及夾中的樂趣。<br />\n<br />\n台灣的夾娃娃機，把這兩個因素都剝奪了。<br />\n<br />\n至於日本這種「按規矩來」的玩法，表面上看起來成本比較高（被夾中機率高），但是能夠激發挑戰與磨練的慾望，在技術上培養出真正的強者，商家也會研發出更多有難度、新奇但不作弊的夾法。<br />\n<br />\n利潤從哪裡來？玩家從菜鳥到達人過程中的學費。最重要的，日本玩法會讓你相信「努力一定有收獲」。台灣玩法則是「幹都給你玩就好啦」。<br />\n<br />\n附圖是抓給女兒的哥吉拉娃娃，我絕對不會說我花了多少枚五百塊⋯我只能說當時隔壁（圖右）有個高中男生三人組，負責夾的用一枚五百塊就夾到寫實版哥吉拉模型⋯"},{"pid":"cf903d5e414581889a12b4a07433d3e7ad682b90","tid":1510413,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T07:27:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PWzcvgg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPWzcvgg.jpg&h=187c67d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8biyC3g8rst4cc2NZsp7q1N1o%3D&h=ad6d23e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8biyC3g8rst4cc2NZsp7q1N1o%3D&h=c46d764a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8biyC3g8rst4cc2NZsp7q1N1o%3D&h=336d9b8f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"2d64c0dc4bd8016f2686314dc8125c8152291195","tid":1510413,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T07:27:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://buzzorange.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/16427343_10154977769117556_6257077965714940370_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbuzzorange.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F02%2F16427343_10154977769117556_6257077965714940370_n.jpg&h=0df8836c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://buzzorange.com/2017/02/07/a-lesson-from-crane-machine/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbuzzorange.com%2F2017%2F02%2F07%2Fa-lesson-from-crane-machine%2F&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8biyC3g8rst4cc2NZsp7q1N1o%3D&h=65cb05cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://buzzorange.com/2017/02/07/a-lesson-from-crane-machine/</a>"},{"pid":"363c93e41512a9665dbf2fe5ed45fa99fbe7ea4a","tid":1510413,"uid":58609,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T07:37:04.000Z","msg":"台灣係玩另一種技術<br />\n<br />\n台灣抓唔似日本果D直上直落,而係可以chok/搖<br />\n台灣大把人靠夾娃娃機賺錢"},{"pid":"908ca83c48a96d705fb4933c2ce0993d0342e45d","tid":1510413,"uid":84119,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"363c93e41512a9665dbf2fe5ed45fa99fbe7ea4a","tid":1510413,"uid":58609,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T07:37:04.000Z","msg":"台灣係玩另一種技術<br />\n<br />\n台灣抓唔似日本果D直上直落,而係可以chok/搖<br />\n台灣大把人靠夾娃娃機賺錢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T07:52:17.000Z","msg":"坐左幾耐？<br />\n<br />\n加左個鐵環防人fing好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a11e2f247497edb99bde948886b22c3e322be0d","tid":1510413,"uid":52299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T07:54:37.000Z","msg":"冇幾耐之前先係日本封左間鋪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42e1345a294ed3f58e01bd756994f9e696f41f5d","tid":1510413,"uid":131522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T07:55:45.000Z","msg":"台日兩國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9504c7be5854963adcdecd90df6b8c72c36148c","tid":1510413,"uid":149342,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T07:58:41.000Z","msg":"都係香港好"},{"pid":"db158e2c11d9961d35e3aa971694f22360a6a119","tid":1510413,"uid":391,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"363c93e41512a9665dbf2fe5ed45fa99fbe7ea4a","tid":1510413,"uid":58609,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T07:37:04.000Z","msg":"台灣係玩另一種技術<br />\n<br />\n台灣抓唔似日本果D直上直落,而係可以chok/搖<br />\n台灣大把人靠夾娃娃機賺錢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T08:17:39.000Z","msg":"睇少啲youtube片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />依家十之有九都冇得fing<br />\n啲youtuber多數都係本身有錢，再靠做台主搵多啲錢"},{"pid":"38c26d8fc612118320c08a2f0f406326c8f66d18","tid":1510413,"uid":308530,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T09:02:50.000Z","msg":"兩個都唔同嘢 點比較<br />\n日本一部機機價幾萬蚊， 你啲台灣機一部幾千蚊仲要淘寶有得賣<br />\n日本機鋪大多放嘅係景品， 台灣就人人平民做機主 自己放獎品入去<br />\n日本幾間大型連鎖 sega taito roundone<br />\n基本上setting都一式一樣，每種本身都有唔同攻略方法<br />\n香港台灣就著重玩三爪保夾， 除非你專登走去香港namco玩 先有少少日本味<br />\n日本係用咗十幾廿年時間去慢慢發展 兩個生態梗係唔同"},{"pid":"45431701e45fbe9895cbc26ace4105370877ba9a","tid":1510413,"uid":268711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a11e2f247497edb99bde948886b22c3e322be0d","tid":1510413,"uid":52299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T07:54:37.000Z","msg":"冇幾耐之前先係日本封左間鋪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T10:15:45.000Z","msg":"係大阪先多細鋪黑店啫<br />\n成個日本大把夾公仔大鋪"},{"pid":"ed95d5da6ce41171d4ed9c4a59998dd004e81313","tid":1510413,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T11:04:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3fbce1b53b61c4205b305593d5e9f64b0b5653b","tid":1510413,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T08:55:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"893848373d1f72abd15b675a21c53bbc0054209a","tid":1510413,"uid":8308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T09:02:09.000Z","msg":"我覺得職員都好大影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n日本D職員見你夾得10次8次 基本上都會幫你調位教埋你夾<br />\n之後基本補多3-4次就會夾到 <br />\n台灣就真係等你保夾先會中"},{"pid":"ebdd43de2db5ad5229e7609fdcd4cc3660c43bdd","tid":1510413,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T09:04:49.000Z","msg":"夾1鋪就知係咪無力抓，有冇得fing"},{"pid":"bdb2b60e0a915491c5ef6f03782c9c7c51fabad2","tid":1510413,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"908ca83c48a96d705fb4933c2ce0993d0342e45d","tid":1510413,"uid":84119,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"363c93e41512a9665dbf2fe5ed45fa99fbe7ea4a","tid":1510413,"uid":58609,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T07:37:04.000Z","msg":"台灣係玩另一種技術<br />\n<br />\n台灣抓唔似日本果D直上直落,而係可以chok/搖<br />\n台灣大把人靠夾娃娃機賺錢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T07:52:17.000Z","msg":"坐左幾耐？<br />\n<br />\n加左個鐵環防人fing好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T09:06:35.000Z","msg":"S 扣唔係部部都有，<br />\n你見有扣都入錢係真心進貢？"},{"pid":"9167238895228958a49237cd062ca641dc8bc954","tid":1510413,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db158e2c11d9961d35e3aa971694f22360a6a119","tid":1510413,"uid":391,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"363c93e41512a9665dbf2fe5ed45fa99fbe7ea4a","tid":1510413,"uid":58609,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T07:37:04.000Z","msg":"台灣係玩另一種技術<br />\n<br />\n台灣抓唔似日本果D直上直落,而係可以chok/搖<br />\n台灣大把人靠夾娃娃機賺錢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T08:17:39.000Z","msg":"睇少啲youtube片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />依家十之有九都冇得fing<br />\n啲youtuber多數都係本身有錢，再靠做台主搵多啲錢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T09:08:05.000Z","msg":"草爺係進口商，拍youtube 係create need"},{"pid":"c50867e3fa1f37cf90a50300aa9197086c274768","tid":1510413,"uid":224510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T09:10:47.000Z","msg":"香港又貴又伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14e9e467b49f983ded502d6a489300c36bc9da3a","tid":1510413,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T09:15:04.000Z","msg":"爭取民主 = 夾公仔<br />\n夾公仔部機永遠都冇力 <br />\n掂到下隻公仔 夾上半空隻爪就會冇力<br />\n隻公仔就跌返落黎 <br />\n<br />\n當你想轉身離開既時候，<br />\n部機同你講：喂呀哥，隻公仔都叫夾到上半空，跌落黎個位離個窿又近左，都叫階段勝利呀<br />\n你唔甘心，所以入多一次錢<br />\n結果一如所料又係半路就跌左落黎<br />\n<br />\n明眼人都知部機呃錢<br />\n但偏偏有啲傻仔不斷入錢落去<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中共每分鐘都會郁d公仔擺返遠d, 搬黎搬去搬龍門咁, 所以從來都無人真係夾到過<br />\n<br />\n唯一方法係暴力打爆部機，先可以成功"},{"pid":"263c261ed04db4302ccc2fbd4057967519334b9d","tid":1510413,"uid":149342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T09:22:40.000Z","msg":"香港日本台灣點排名？"},{"pid":"ce8f4628c63b986f213236ac71fcdbbe6e096734","tid":1510413,"uid":26773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T09:45:54.000Z","msg":"有無玩過旺角連儂牆個間?<br />\n個夾上到去會向右大力fing<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f366d442fb5721e29849233cc83cad9d8a3d554","tid":1510413,"uid":224510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce8f4628c63b986f213236ac71fcdbbe6e096734","tid":1510413,"uid":26773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T09:45:54.000Z","msg":"有無玩過旺角連儂牆個間?<br />\n個夾上到去會向右大力fing<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T09:48:41.000Z","msg":"未計機同公仔<br />\n租都攪到蝕啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fec0deb8387739edd41e3f6774a1aa49065a1a8","tid":1510413,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T10:16:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}